Syntype NHM type 1092 incomplete, gravid female, with 210 chaetigers, L10 = 9.3 mm, W10 = 5 mm TL = 860 mm (Fig. 
5A-C
). Anterior region with dorsum convex, flat ventre (Fig. 
5C, E
); body depressed from chaetiger 13 (Fig. 
5C, E
), widest at chaetiger 51, tapering after chaetiger 173.

